                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1101546440" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1101546440">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaobaiii/">不如归去</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-11-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">尼玛越读越被鲍曼的悲观主义敲打</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1049073968">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1049073968" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1049073968" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1049073968">有用</a>
