      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="19869695">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sandlee1986/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1132830-6.jpg" alt="剧旁" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19869695/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19869695/" class="">第124页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sandlee1986/" class=" " title="剧旁">剧旁</a>
                (你巨胖)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19869695">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">阿伦特说：“穷人心底的期望不是‘按照人们的需要进行分配’，而是‘按照人们的愿望进行分配’。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-23 21:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>阿伦特说：“穷人心底的期望不是‘按照人们的需要进行分配’，而是‘按照人们的愿望进行分配’。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







